data.enText: a road or the part of a road used by vehicles

tr: a road (especially that part of a road) over which vehicles travel

value.def: The roadway is the part of a road that is used by traffic.

example.ex: Marks in the roadway seem to indicate that he skidded taking a sharp turn.
example.tran: 从车道上的痕迹来看，他似乎在急转弯时打滑了。
